comments: Stevens (CLE) jumps A-B and makes makes contact to the body of Brazdeikis (ORL) that does affects his shot at the basket.
Brazdeikis (ORL) makes marginal body contact with Stevens (CLE) at the start of the drive.
Bamba (ORL) legally blocks Stevens' (CLE) driving shot attempt.
Markkanen (CLE) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Okeke (ORL) before making legal contact to the ball.
Bamba (ORL) grabs Markkanen's (CLE) left shoulder during the rebound and pulls him off of his spot, which affects his ability to retrieve the ball.
LeVert (CLE) makes contact with Brazdeikis' (ORL) off-hand that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Okoro (CLE) commits a five-second violation on the in-bounds play.
LeVert (CLE) makes marginal contact to Bamba's (ORL) arm as he is passing the ball.
Markkanen (CLE) commits a take foul on Hampton (ORL).
Markkanen (CLE) commits a take foul on Cannady (ORL).
